VignetteBuilder: knitr
Description: Functions for power analysis and sample size calculation. Examples are Welch and Hsu t-Tests, Wilcoxon Rank Sum and Signed Rank Tests as well as power and sample size required for the evaluation of a diagnostic test(-system).
